OL,3,CMet Police chief grabs microphone
OL,4,Cafter two-tier policing question
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley grabbed a journalist's
OL,8,Fmicrophone and threw it to the ground
OL,9,Fas he left an emergency Cobra meeting
OL,10,Fon Monday.
OL,12,FIt came after the reporter asked him:
OL,13,F"Are you going to end two-tier
OL,14,Fpolicing?"
OL,16,FSir Mark could be seen reaching out
OL,17,Ftowards the microphone, grabbing a
OL,18,Fpart of it and throwing it to the
OL,19,Fground before leaving without saying
OL,20,Fanything.
