OL,3,CMet Police chief grabs microphone
OL,4,Cafter two-tier policing question
OL,6,FDowning Street has already rejected
OL,7,FNigel Farage's claim that there is
OL,8,F"two-tier policing" in Britain, where
OL,9,Fright-wing protests are dealt with
OL,10,Fmore harshly than left-wing ones.
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer's official spokesman
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Prime Minister wouldn't
OL,14,Frecognise that characterisation of
OL,15,Fpolicing.
OL,17,F"The job of the police is to keep
OL,18,Feveryone safe, to tackle violence and
OL,19,Fdisorder no matter the origination."
