OL,3,CMet Police chief grabs microphone
OL,4,Cafter two-tier policing question
OL,6,FThe Cobra meeting was called after
OL,7,Fviolent disorder across the country,
OL,8,Fwhere some rioters tried to storm
OL,9,Fhotels housing asylum seekers.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer said a "standing
OL,12,Farmy" of specialist police officers
OL,13,Fwould be set up to deal with rioting
OL,14,Fand unrest.
OL,16,FSpeaking after an emergency Cobra
OL,17,Fmeeting, the Prime Minister said:
OL,18,F"There are a number of actions that
OL,19,Fcame out of the meeting.
