OL,3,CMet Police chief grabs microphone
OL,4,Cafter two-tier policing question
OL,6,F"The first is we will have a standing
OL,7,Farmy of specialist public duty
OL,8,Fofficers so that we will have enough
OL,9,Fofficers to deal with this where we
OL,10,Fneed them.
OL,12,F"The second is we will ramp up
OL,13,Fcriminal justice. There have already
OL,14,Fbeen hundreds of arrests, some have
OL,15,Fappeared in court this morning.
OL,17,F"I have asked for early consideration
OL,18,Fof the earliest naming and
OL,19,Fidentification of those involved in
OL,20,Fthe process who will feel the full
OL,21,Fforce of the law."
